data.description:
Without a doubt the best place to live! Close to ikea, sawgrass mills mall and the bb&t center! Not to mention sawgrass elementary school is right around the corner! This tucked away water front villa offers an open floor plan, upgraded appliances including dual oven range and garbage disposal, a 1st floor master w/ huge walk in closet..And a balcony off each upper bedroom.  Grab it while its still available! As-is, or completely painted, maintenced and cleaned for $2000.

(RLNE2565188)
